00:32:19.749 --> 00:32:24.460
of decision making it's foolish; it's crazy.
Like, "I used to be someone who tried to tell

00:32:24.460 --> 00:32:28.180
the truth then my Mom came down the stairs
on the way to a party and asked me if she

00:32:28.180 --> 00:32:31.989
looked nice in a dress and I said yes, so
I now I lie at every available opportunity."

00:32:31.989 --> 00:32:32.989
[laughter]

00:32:32.989 --> 00:32:33.989
&gt;&gt;female in audience: Right.

00:32:33.989 --> 00:32:34.989
[laughter]

00:32:34.989 --> 00:32:35.989
&gt;&gt;Jonathan Safran Foer: It just doesn't make
