00:32:35.989 --> 00:32:36.989
[laughter]

00:32:36.989 --> 00:32:39.279
And so I think guiding the conversation toward
the middle ground like, "You know what I've

00:32:39.279 --> 00:32:45.110
been thinking about this and Jesus, it matters
