00:32:51.879 --> 00:32:55.434
some things are just wrong. And this is wrong.
I know what's goin' on is wrong. So I'm trying

00:32:55.434 --> 00:32:56.580
to eat less of it."

00:32:56.580 --> 00:32:59.710
I think that is actually a very successful
approach.

00:32:59.710 --> 00:33:00.710
&gt;&gt;female in audience: Yeah.

00:33:00.710 --> 00:33:04.590
&gt;&gt;Jonathan Safran Foer: Because it doesn't
make the-the other person the topic of your

00:33:04.590 --> 00:33:05.590
conversation.

00:33:05.590 --> 00:33:09.799
&gt;&gt;female in audience: I-I guess I just think
