00:33:16.690 --> 00:33:20.950
tradition that this factory farming piece
has been a part of the picture, I mean --

00:33:20.950 --> 00:33:24.159
&gt;&gt;Jonathan Safran Foer: But you also have
other traditions and cultures like caring,

00:33:24.159 --> 00:33:25.159
like --

00:33:25.159 --> 00:33:26.159
&gt;&gt;female in audience: Right.

00:33:26.159 --> 00:33:29.940
&gt;&gt;Jonathan Safran Foer: like some people find
