00:33:35.549 --> 00:33:36.549
actually teach the same lessons--

00:33:36.549 --> 00:33:37.549
&gt;&gt;female in audience: Right.

00:33:37.549 --> 00:33:40.450
&gt;&gt;Jonathan Safran Foer: about like dominion
