00:37:08.120 --> 00:37:09.120
[laughter]

00:37:09.120 --> 00:37:10.120
Republicans?

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:11.120
[laughter]

00:37:11.120 --> 00:37:15.460
There's a big difference between that and
