00:42:39.310 --> 00:42:40.590
Bay Aquarium Seafood Watch Card for-for seafood.

00:42:40.590 --> 00:42:48.680
So every time I go to a restaurant or I-I'm
eating fish somewhere I look up to see that

00:42:48.680 --> 00:42:51.250
fish species and it's totally revolutionized
